    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 / 0.26)
    v2 = (v0 - 0.13)
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.41) / 0.24) / 0.90)
    v2 = wp.cos((0.10 * wp.sin(v2 + 0.86)))
    v1 = (0.61 + ((v0 + 0.03 - tmp + 0.82) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.65)))
